thread.title: Michael Krowicki

author: Michael Krowicki
title: Michael Krowicki
text: The crew here is just INCREDIBLE !!!! Need help finding something they are right there with no hesitations. The store was PACKED for the Canyon sale but everything was in it's place and CLEAN , variety and prices are GREAT !!! The Manager ( Ryan McCloskey ) was pleasant , very well spoken and just a downright NICE guy ! VERY, VERY tight ship he's running there ;)
